{"tid":2234400,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"觀塘兩司機互毆 旅遊巴司機被扑頭昏迷","createTime":"2020-10-08T01:15:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-08T02:53:35.000Z","uid":44209,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7ff2cc74b06df3419c74acf546c7f1641b198be7","tid":2234400,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T01:15:23.000Z","msg":"扑頭分分鐘可大可小<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n觀塘裕民坊停車場對開一組交通燈，早上7時15分，一名小巴司機與一名旅遊巴司機，疑因事發生爭執，其後動武，旅巴司機被人用硬物扑頭，當場倒地昏迷，另一司機亦報稱不適，二人俱送院救治，警員接報到場，將案件列襲擊案，正調查事件原因。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201008/76NRZOXUQBAPRJDJIXJAVENMF4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201008%2F76NRZOXUQBAPRJDJIXJAVENMF4%2F&d=xM4HlgsByf6UCiwKp%2FWW5IICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=2a93a183\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201008%2F76NRZOXUQBAPRJDJIXJAVENMF4%2F&h=1fb39858\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201008/76NRZOXUQBAPRJDJIXJAVENMF4/</a>"},{"pid":"3d0b0b7778beeedbdff806e8b8663ee58e6f232b","tid":2234400,"uid":65952,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T01:20:00.000Z","msg":"小巴司機 你撐唔撐警？撐警就唔駛驚了"},{"pid":"e2d159fb3f376295854a2f762a0c52fc6c04dd97","tid":2234400,"uid":44209,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3d0b0b7778beeedbdff806e8b8663ee58e6f232b","tid":2234400,"uid":65952,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T01:20:00.000Z","msg":"小巴司機 你撐唔撐警？撐警就唔駛驚了"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T01:22:03.000Z","msg":"唔係講笑，之前有單，有個大快活阿姐俾人扑頭打劫，仲走去返工，轉過頭就死咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57faaa50cbe1e17534c9e16e37064113faa51929","tid":2234400,"uid":121197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T01:23:18.000Z","msg":"咁呢個時候士巴拿係咪叫藏有攻擊性武器"},{"pid":"3088bdd1d1c28d9b47e936397d2600b070657941",